舟、\r\n    車、航空機內而犯之。\r\n前項之未遂犯罰之。\r\n\r\n附件：","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c971%2c20220906%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗簡,971,20220906,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"971","JDATE":"20220906","JTITLE":"加重竊盜"}